_:N442cefbe20564ba7a4268a78dec421ec <http://schema.org/name> "Emma Ferguson-Gould" .
_:N442cefbe20564ba7a4268a78dec421ec <http://schema.org/mainEntityOfPage> <https://www.gov.uk/government/people/emma-ferguson-gould--2> .
_:N442cefbe20564ba7a4268a78dec421ec <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Emma joined the Nuclear Restoration Services Ltd Board in November 2023 as a NDA Nominated Non-Executive Director. </p>\n\n<p>Emma joined the NDA as Group Chief Commercial and Business Development Officer in February 2022 from BEIS where she was the Commercial and Operations Director and a Non-executive Director for UK Shared Business Services Ltd. Emma brings with her a wealth of cross-sector commercial experience obtained in both leadership and delivery roles across Whitehall and the private sector</p>\n\n<p>Emma is a member of the Company’s Safety, Security Health &amp; Environment Committee and a member of the Nominations &amp; Remuneration Committee.</p>\n" .
